flowchart TD

    USER["User Query"]

    OA["Orchestrator
    (Direct vs Pipeline)"]

    SUP["Supervisor
    - Routing
    - Query Rewrite"]

    DISC["Discovery
    - Web Search
    - FAISS Filter"]

    CP2["CP-2 HITL
    Startup Selection"]

    MINI["Mini Supervisor
    (Pass-through)"]

    TECH["Tech Summary"]
    MARKET["Market Eval"]
    COMP["Competitor"]

    JUDGE["Judge Loop
    (5 Criteria)"]

    REWORK["Rework
    (Max 3 Iterations)"]

    DEC["Decision
    (Scorecard + CP-4)"]

    REPORT["Report Generation
    (Parallel Sections + Reflection)"]

    CP5["CP-5 HITL"]

    END["Final Output"]

    %% Flow
    USER --> OA
    OA -->|pipeline| SUP
    OA -->|direct| END

    SUP -->|no candidates| DISC
    DISC --> CP2
    CP2 --> SUP

    SUP -->|analysis needed| MINI

    MINI --> TECH
    MINI --> MARKET
    MINI --> COMP

    TECH --> SUP
    MARKET --> SUP
    COMP --> SUP

    SUP -->|analysis complete| JUDGE

    JUDGE -->|fail| REWORK
    REWORK --> SUP

    JUDGE -->|pass| DEC
    DEC --> REPORT
    REPORT --> CP5
    CP5 --> END